By Shahar Jacob

==================
=  Description:  =
==================
This is a program that aligned images. its mean that we gets
an image, checking what is the dominant angle, and return a new image that
rotate in the dominant angle.

For using, put parameters in this way: images/imageToLoad.jpg nameToSave.jpg MaxSizeOfDiagonal
For example: images/test45.jpg output.jpg 330
You need to run the file aligned.py.
Enjoy.

The file aligned_helper.py was provided by the course staff and its main target is to convert an image into pixels.


